data.description: UNDER $200k for one of the cutest bungalows in Kingfisher on the market.  The charm and character this home has to offer is what sets this beauty apart from the others.  Stepping in the front door your eye will be drawn to the beautiful hardwood floors, arched doorways, & built-in storage nooks. 2 bedrooms on the main level with full bath. 3rd bedroom and bath on the 2nd level. With excellent flow this home has very little unused space. Oversized living & dining room. Kitchen with breakfast nook. 2nd living room with easy access to the wrap around back porch.  Bonus finished basement would make the ideal rec. room or home office. Sellers are in the process of replacing roof from April 2023 hailstorm as well as any damaged windows screens. Schedule your showing today!
